dct_description_sm: Relief shown by form lines, and spot heights. Map shows two classes of roads, railways, electric transmission lines, post offices, "Issued by Authority of the Hon. Eric Reece, Minister for Lands and Works." "Crown copyright reserved". "The Nomenclature on this map has been approved by the Nomenclature Board of Tasmania in parts only." "This map is not the result of precise survey and should not be regarded as entirely accurate. The representation of a road or track on this map is no evidence of the existence of a right of way." "Magnetic Variation in the centre of this sheet is about 12 30' E. Annual Change is about 07' E." "Boundaries shown are drawn from latest information available but are not necessarily correct."
